orithm to the stochastic setting and achieve the optimal convergence rate in both bi-SC-SC and bi-C-SC settings. AG-OG is the first single-call algorithm with optimal convergence rates in both deterministic and stochastic settings for bilinearly coupled minimax optimization problems.", "authors": [{"author": {"author_id": "adda08ceab9325a6fa8398276e2529a0", "name": "Chris Junchi Li", "links": [{"type": "openreview", "link": "~Chris_Junchi_Li1"}, {"type": "semantic_scholar", "link": "2109460766"}]}, "affiliations": [{"institution_id": "1b1277c14cfee149562b4bd94ea490ad", "name": "Department of Electrical Engineering", "category": "unknown"}, {"institution_id": "47114d77571f2b96dcc886ae0e72de12", "name": "University of California", "category": "unknown"}]}, {"author": {"author_id": "5fd46ca16df46b4bd6663977b0497d76", "name": "Huizhuo Yuan", "links": []}, "affiliations": []}, {"author": {"author_id": "ec7c49bd02506d08c4ab7e68abf179b9", "name": "Angela Yuan", "links": [{"type": "openreview", "link": "~Angela_Yuan1"}, {"type": "semantic_scholar", "link": "2162072451"}]}, "affiliations": [{"institution_id": "200bed81461cad607d593360fe5fcc0a", "name": "Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al", "category": "unknown"}, {"institution_id": "5aba91d6a514aff0054d48b987c3fea6", "name": "DIRO", "category": "unknown"}, {"institution_id": "78a83265183550c66a78ff9b5f9b960f", "name": "Mila", "category": "unknown"}]}, {"author": {"author_id": "9c81d52a835b574e15d59d9b39254580", "name": "Gauthier Gidel", "links": [{"type": "bio", "link": "gauthier-gidel"}, {"type": "email.mila", "link": "gidelgau@mila.quebec"}, {"type": "mag", "link": "2539484857"}, {"type": "openreview", "link": "~Gauthier_Gidel1"}, {"type": "semantic_scholar", "link": "8150760"}, {"type": "wpid_en", "link": "56939"}, {"type": "wpid_fr", "link": "56938"}]}, "affiliations": [{"institution_id": "200bed81461cad607d593360fe5fcc0a", "name": "Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al", "category": "unknown"}, {"institution_id": "4374964384fb